race.description: Book Your Xmas Party 3rd or 10th Dec Hcp (Bm60)
race.comment: NGAPALI BEACH (3) presents third-up and is poised to find her best with the key jockey switch to Darmanin. Was beaten 1.6L this track/trip last time in tougher grade and maps well. The one to beat. STARS IN THE NIGHT (4) led here first-up and looked a run short, beaten 1.5L. She draws inside and keeps a handy 2kg claim. She's only won 1/7 over this longer sprint but has more to give and is sure to give a big sight. NAZORIAN (6) improved sharply second-up in the same contest beaten a nose. He's had a trial since and is proven third-up. He's also a niggle at 1200m but should get every chance to run it right out. POWER MAGNUM (7) was beaten 1.6L in that race back from the synthetic. The inside gate will advantage and he's in the mix.
